HEADWORD: Bombolo
<hw>Bom"bo*lo</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Bomboloes</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Cf. It
<ets>bombola</ets> a pitcher.]</ety> <def>A thin spheroidal glass retort
or flask, used in the sublimation of camphor.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>bumbelo</asp>, and <asp>bumbolo</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
